267
00:11:53,947 --> 00:11:55,524
We've got to keep him
in the sheltered area

268
00:11:55,548 --> 00:11:57,380
till he learns some sense.

269
00:11:57,450 --> 00:11:59,028
Don't they have those stripes
in Pentonville, then?

270
00:11:59,052 --> 00:12:00,930
Oh, yeah. Just never
