281
00:12:23,543 --> 00:12:25,102
You get 21 days, right?

282
00:12:25,178 --> 00:12:27,340
Yeah, they just said
me time went on pause.

283
00:12:27,413 --> 00:12:30,281
Well, if your time went on
pause, when did it start again?

284
00:12:30,350 --> 00:12:31,613
When I got back to me pad.

285
00:12:31,684 --> 00:12:34,620
No way.
You got 21 days extra.

286
00:12:34,687 --> 00:12:36,622
They got to be doubled.

287
00:12:36,689 --> 00:12:39,955
You sure about that?
How long would he have?

288
00:12:40,026 --> 00:12:42,291
I don't know.

289
00:12:42,362 --> 00:12:43,955
Piss off!

290
00:12:46,366 --> 00:12:48,699
There's money in this for you.

291
00:12:48,768 --> 00:12:50,999
Get it sent to your wife.

292
00:12:52,038 --> 00:12:55,270
You sure it'd take 20 minutes
before the scream went up?

293
00:12:55,341 --> 00:12:57,469
